author: @soundaryashanthi2548
text: The recent code available focuses only on acoustic analysis (extraction of mel spectrograms) and the CNN-based classification part, which is one aspect of ASR. ASR involves additional complexities like language modeling, decoding sequences, handling language grammar, and using language models using language modeling techniques, decoding algorithms (like HMM or sequence models), and possibly incorporate attention mechanisms or RNN-based architectures that handle sequential data.
